      <textAnnotation id="sid-9D49F276-8E00-4C70-9675-8366CAA231A2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>KDD: Mask Part Numbers
We will create part numbers by mask type.  Transactions will be at the type level (e.g., 5 of type 1, 3 of type 2) vs. individual masks.  Pricing and standard costs will be maintained at the type level
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-50543C0E-EE66-48C7-9D33-9618137FA530" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Except: 
India, China, Brazil, Argentina, Russia
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2F653522-9A1F-40B2-9B40-22FD5CB83A06" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
